OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day with some
OL,6,Fgood sunny spells through the day.
OL,7,FVery warm with light winds, but
OL,8,Fslightly breezier on the east coast.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA dry, warm and bright
OL,11,Fevening with some hazy sunny periods.
OL,12,FIt will then remain dry for the rest
OL,13,Fof the night with clear spells and
OL,14,Flight winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FEarly morning cloud soon
OL,17,Fburning off to leave another very warm
OL,18,Fand largely sunny day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
